ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一票不投胡國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9e39e0c6f4e809650ed696627479f3dc79830f","tid":112853,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"完全冇實據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43224586c4f4d77b5f03d391a1350ba5c4576510","tid":112853,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全冇實據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺何志光既世界係唔需要西方法庭既證據<br />\n佢仲活係卡通片既世界<br />\n勇者（主角即自己）一眼就洞悉魔王既心思<br />\n跟住就出死光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884186d154104212219e9003e6283bb6579bad41","tid":112853,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/224923_1ebb8b209fd44c50e8f4a1541206ea16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F224923_1ebb8b209fd44c50e8f4a1541206ea16.jpg&h=8b755811&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港海關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇投考秘笈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a019bc6931beb443e107b9ff07794dfde8ae081","tid":112853,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:32:54.000Z",